  "description": [
    "Gossip About Famous Folk Of the Hour SENATOR MATTHEW STANLEY QUAY whose illness is causing his friends much anxiety had a good many experiences as a young man before he found out that he possessed a genius for controlling political affairs As a youth of eighteen he began lecturing on astronomy and after that taught school for a time but this did not prove a congenial occupa tion so he started west intending to fight the Indians and finally joined a Texas organization which was to wipe out the Comanche tribe Owing to lack of an appropriation by the legisla ture the soldiers did not go on the warpath and without doing any fight ing the future political warrior return ed to Pennsylvania there to take up the more peaceful though sometimes turbulent profession of the lawyer He had begun the study of law on gradu ating from Jefferson coliego several years before In 1854 he was admit ted to the bar and at that time began his political career just a half century ago Quays first political aliiiiations were with the Pro hibitionists II i s civil war experi ences soon follow SENATOR QUAY ed He held several responsible"
  ],
